*2025 
import delimited co2025a.txt, clear 
rename (v2 v3 v4 v6 v8 v11 v14 v17) /// 
	(statefips countyfips region county one two threefour five)
drop in 1/3
gen scfips = statefips + countyfips
destring one two threefour five, replace
gen mm25 = two + threefour
gen tot25 = one + two + threefour + five 
gen pmm25 = mm25 / tot25
keep statefips countyfips scfips region county mm25 tot25 pmm25 
save co2025a.dta, replace 

